00:08:10.380 --> 00:08:12.240
Some of you are probably
familiar with this,

00:08:12.240 --> 00:08:15.690
and I'm probably preaching
here to the crowd, but I feel

00:08:15.690 --> 00:08:20.610
that it's important anyway
to emphasize this point,

00:08:20.610 --> 00:08:24.640
that when speaking of accessibility,
we're speaking of users

00:08:24.640 --> 00:08:28.930
that have specific needs
or-- I'm losing the word.

00:08:33.850 --> 00:08:35.440
